text: Rhagodeya is a genus of solifuges or sun spiders.Biolib == Species == This genus includes two species from Libya, Somalia and Sudan: * Rhagodeya nigra Caporiacco, 1937 * Rhagodeya nubia Roewer, 1933 The Arachnid Order Solifugae == References == Category:Solifugae genera Category:Arachnids of Africa
title: Rhagodeya
